													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/hebaalaghaandjuliachoucairvizoso/">Heba Al-Agha and Julia Choucair Vizoso</a></h6>
													<b>Heba Al-Agha</b> is a mother, writer, and creative writing educator at the A.M. Qattan Foundation in Gaza City. Her work has appeared in English translation in ArabLit Quarterly.
<br></br>
<b>Julia Choucair Vizoso</b> is an independent scholar and seasonal translator. She hopes Heba Al-Agha’s words move you to refuse and resist the Israel-US genocide of the Palestinian people and destruction of Lebanon, wherever and however you can.																									</div>
